## What This Case Teaches About Different Incident Scenarios

This case is specifically about MFA access loss. But the methodology applies to:

- **Security incidents:** Not just remediate the compromise, build prevention and detection
- **Performance incidents:** Not just optimize performance, understand why it degraded and build alerting
- **Cost incidents:** Not just reduce spend, understand why costs grew and build governance
- **Compliance incidents:** Not just fix the violation, understand why the control failed and strengthen it

**The pattern is always the same:** 
Incident → Root Cause Analysis → Process Improvement → Prevention Framework → Stronger Customer Relationship

