## How This Connects to Your Customer Lifecycle

### During Onboarding (Months 1–3)
Preventive work: "Let's build your offboarding checklist for IAM/MFA. When someone leaves, 
here's what we validate."

### During Adoption (Months 4–9)
Continuous improvement: "Let's audit your access. Are there roles with more permissions 
than they need? Are there accounts that should have MFA but don't?"

### During an Incident (Whenever)
Relationship deepening: "We fixed the immediate problem. Let's use this as a learning 
opportunity. Here's what this tells us about your operating model."

### During Retention/Renewal (Month 12+)
Trust signal: "We've worked together on incidents. You've built processes that prevent 
recurrence. That's the kind of partnership that makes sense to renew."

